name: Twi'lek LoRA
description:
Model based on Star Wars Twi'lek race. Trained on AOM-2 model. It has a lot of potential and wanted to share it with others to see what others can make!

For absolute best results, mix both version 1 and 2 ~0.4

It was trained to use "Twilek and alien" as trigger words, but noticed best results just used "colored skin" and "____ skin" (red/blue/green/etc)

Weight are generally at 1.0 for the LoRA. Please share your creations!
